list.abstract: after，英文单词，词性有介词、连词、副词、形容词；作为介词时意思为有……后的；（表示时间）在……以后；（表示位置、顺序）在……后面；作为连词是的意思为在……以后；作为副词的意思为以后，继后；作为形容词是的意思为后来的，以后的。
AFTER是由成都阿尔法特机械设备有限公司于2019年02月14日创建成立的五金工具品牌，以从事数控系统、精密行星减速、多轴EtherCat总线控制器、工业机器人控制器、全系列交流伺服驱动器、全系列数控车床、数控铣床、加工中心及工业自动化产品研发、生产及营销服务。

yingyinNormal.en: Before or after he freed Ireland?
yingyinNormal.zh: 在他解放爱尔兰之前还是之后？

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, but after that, we're shooting some pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，不过之后要打球。

yingyinNormal.en: We can take these round there after lunch.
yingyinNormal.zh: 午餐之后我们把这些送过去。

yingyinNormal.en: When did you meet my mother? Not long after.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你什么时候遇到我母亲的？就在这不久之后。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, there you are. you disappeared after dinner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，你在这里。你在晚餐之后就消失了。

yingyinNormal.en: Tomorrow afternoon after Mr. Fornum's been executed?
yingyinNormal.zh: 明天下午，佛努姆先生执行死刑之后?

yingyinNormal.en: We can take these round there after lunch. Oh, goody.
yingyinNormal.zh: 午餐之后我们把这些送过去。噢，太好了。

yingyinNormal.en: And what happened after this photograph was taken, Detective?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这张照片拍完之后发生了什么，警探？

yingyinNormal.en: After the brothers went to sleep, I heard loud voices.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当他们几兄弟都睡着之后，我听到很吵的声音。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm surprised you have an appetite after meeting with Dunbar.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很惊讶你在见过邓巴之后居然还有胃口。

yingyinNormal.en: After initiations, rankings will determine what jobs you move into.
yingyinNormal.zh: 入会训练过后你们的排名将决定你们之后的工作。

yingyinNormal.en: After the snap. Before the snap. After. Before. Now, does it really matter? Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是在传球之前。在传球之后之后。之前。这很重要吗？对。

yingyinNormal.en: And after that? After that you're on a plane, back at work Monday morning. No one is the wiser.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在这之后呢？之后你周一早上飞回去上班，神不知鬼不觉。

yingyinNormal.en: 48 hours after administration, but after that it should work perfectly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是前48小时，之后一切都会运行正常。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, it was so amazing. After the love making... Oh my.
yingyinNormal.zh: 感觉好棒，做完爱之后…天哪。

yingyinNormal.en: And the Orcs that remain? We'll take care of them later. After they've ravaged the entire kingdom?
yingyinNormal.zh: 剩下的兽人呢？我们之后再来对付他们。在他们已经破坏了整个王国之后？

yingyinNormal.en: All right, what'd you do after you turned on the defroster?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，那你打开除霜器之后又做了什么？

yingyinNormal.en: After about 90 minutes of proving, it's set for the oven.
yingyinNormal.zh: 90分钟的发酵之后，可以放到烤箱了。

yingyinNormal.en: He certainly kept an annoyingly close watch on me after that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从那之后他就很令人厌烦的监视着我。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, it was after the party, we were on the balcony...
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，就在派对结束之后 我们在阳台上……

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: following in time, place, or order

examination_example.sentence: Both apps, however, were later scrapped, <highlight>after</highlight> Microsoft said it had used their best features in its own products.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，这两个应用程序后来都被废弃了，因为微软表示，它已经在自己的产品中使用了它们最好的功能。

examination_example.sentence: He found a dream job <highlight>after</highlight> graduating from college.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他大学毕业后找到了一份理想的工作。

examination_example.sentence: I assumed that phase was something experts developed <highlight>after</highlight> years of research into children's behaviour: wrong.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我认为这个阶段是专家们在对儿童行为进行多年研究后得出的结论是错的。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>After</highlight> all, it was rumoured that smoking caused cancer for years before the evidence was found to prove a connection.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 毕竟，在证据被发现证明两者有联系之前，有传言说吸烟导致癌症已经很多年了。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>After</highlight> all, if everyone you know is going to college in the fall, it seems silly to stay back a year, doesn't it?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 毕竟，如果每一个人都去念大学，似乎延迟一年读大学是一件很愚蠢的事，不是吗？

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>After</highlight> all, other countries, such as Australia and Britain, have started liberalizing their legal professions.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 毕竟，其他国家，如澳大利亚和英国，已经开始放开他们的法律职业。

sense_info_list.en: next to and following in order or importance

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>After</highlight> the Netherlands, Britain is Europe's most crowded country.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 英国是欧洲仅次于荷兰最拥挤的国家。

examination_example.sentence: Popularity usually comes <highlight>after</highlight> quality.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 受欢迎程度通常在质量之后。

sense_info_list.en: typical of or similar to the style of

examination_example.sentence: This impact will be through a larger group of publishing places that may want to model their approach <highlight>after</highlight> Science.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这种影响出现在一个更大的出版机构群，他们可能希望在《科学》之后以他们的方法为模板。

examination_example.sentence: Instead, they look <highlight>after</highlight> their wellbeing instinctively, and usually more effectively than we do as grownups.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 相反，他们本能地照顾自己的幸福，而且通常比我们成年人更有效。

sense_info_list.en: used when giving someone or something the same name as another person or thing

word_usage.usage:
after后接一段时间，更多用于谈论过去，如：After a few minutes he stopped.几分钟后，他停了下来（描述过去的情况）。
in后接一段时间，更多用于谈论将来，如：He'll be here in a few minutes.几分钟后他会来这里。
after可以用作副词，但只能接在 soon, not long, shortly等时间副词之后。

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 日复一日(表示动作或状态的重复)

examination_example.sentence: She was too exhausted to write <highlight>after</highlight> a busy day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 忙碌了一天后，她筋疲力尽，无法写作。

examination_example.sentence: The hot spring at the foot of the mountain is something you must try <highlight>after</highlight> the climb.

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>After</highlight> a short way, the farmer stopped and pointed at a weed which we missed.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 走了一小段路后，农夫停下脚步，指着我们错过的一片杂草。

examination_example.sentence: Who will look <highlight>after</highlight> the children?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 谁来照看孩子们？

examination_example.sentence: Things quickly got very intense due to the huge amount of energy required to look <highlight>after</highlight> them.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 由于照顾他们需要大量的精力，事情很快变得非常紧张。

examination_example.sentence: And secondly, let me ask you to please look <highlight>after</highlight> your money.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 其次，请你照看好你的钱。

examination_example.sentence: Nobody's going to clean up <highlight>after</highlight> you.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 没人会替你收拾残局的。

examination_example.sentence: Yeah, two days <highlight>after</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 是的，两天后。

examination_example.sentence: If you're worried about taking classes one <highlight>after</highlight> another in different buildings, a quick test run won't hurt.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你担心在不同的大楼里一个接一个地上课，快速试跑一下也无妨。

examination_example.sentence: In study <highlight>after</highlight> study, it appears that these chemical conversations help the neighbors.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一项又一项研究表明，这些化学信息似乎对临近的（神经细胞）有所助益。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: after以过去为起点，表示 “（过去）一段时间以后”，常用于过去时态的句子；after与时间点连用时，也可用于将来时。
in以现在为起点，表示“（将来）一段时间以后”，常用于将来时态的句子。

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 片刻之后；一会后；一阵子之后

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>After</highlight> class, remember to review what you have learned by reading your notes or making a mind map.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 课后，记得通过阅读你的笔记或制作思维导图来复习所学内容。

examination_example.sentence: How did the young man feel <highlight>after</highlight> he heard what old man's said?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 年轻人听了老人的话后感觉如何?

examination_example.sentence: Chinese people are used to napping <highlight>after</highlight> lunch.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 中国人习惯在午饭后午睡。

examination_example.sentence: Boys and girls, you should look <highlight>after</highlight> yourselves when your parents are not at home.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 孩子们，你们父母不在家的时候，你们应该照顾好自己。

examination_example.sentence: Can you look <highlight>after</highlight> my apartment while I'm away?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我不在的时候，你能照看一下我的公寓吗？

examination_example.sentence: The old woman's three sons have all died, and Sally couldn't leave her alone where nobody could look <highlight>after</highlight> her.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这位老妇人的三个儿子都去世了，萨莉不能把她一个人留在一个无人照顾的地方。

sense_info_list.en: used when giving someone or something the same name as another person or thing

examination_example.sentence: The food was usually named <highlight>after</highlight> the dragon.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 食物通常以龙的名字命名。

examination_example.sentence: Mars is the fourth planet from the sun in our solar system and is named <highlight>after</highlight> Mars, the Roman god of war.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 火星是太阳系中距离太阳第四远的行星，以罗马战神火星命名。

examination_example.sentence: I heard that the teahouse was named <highlight>after</highlight> Lao She.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我听说那家茶馆是以老舍的名字命名的。

examination_example.sentence: She knew nothing about seed genetics (遗传学) <highlight>after</highlight> all.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 毕竟她对种子遗传学一无所知。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>After</highlight> all, waste not, want not.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 毕竟，不浪费，不愁缺。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>After</highlight> all, it was the first (one) time for them to see something like that.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 毕竟，这是他们第一次看到这样的事情。

word_usage.usage:
after作连词连接时间状语从句时，从句中一般用现在时表示将来。
示例：I'll tell him after you leave.
你走之后我会告诉他。
after用作副词时常与soon，ever搭配，通常用于表示时间的名词后。

注意after和in的使用：从某时到多久以后，不用after，而用in。如果指“某个时刻，日期或事件以后”，用after。
示例：(1) He will arrive in four weeks.
他将于四周内抵达。
(2) He will arrive after four o'clock.
他将于4点后抵达。
